      origin: 'Yale Center for Emotional Intelligence (RULER framework)',
      shortDesc: 'A 100-square grid based on Russell\'s Circumplex (energy axis × pleasantness axis), color-coded into 4 quadrants: Yellow (high-energy pleasant: excited, joyful), Red (high-energy unpleasant: angry, anxious), Blue (low-energy unpleasant: sad, hopeless), Green (low-energy pleasant: calm, content). Comes with a Mood Meter app.',
