      whenToUse: 'For middle and high school students. When you want a research-grounded color-coded tool. As part of RULER implementation. For adult SEL.',
      research: 'Brackett & Rivers on emotional intelligence; Mood Meter app studies; Hoffmann et al. on RULER outcomes for adolescents.'
